，全民共同抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態緊急，如策劃任何工業行動必需經過既定程序。故此是次問卷將於1月31日23:59截止。希望同業們積極參與此調查，讓金總能全面理解金融界僱主於防疫措施現況，以及會員和同業於共同抗疫的意願，以制定下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtoVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=3502d5db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/toVdkp2QMVwtZXVr7</a><br />\n<br />\n原post傳送門：<br />\n［行動］［請置頂］全民白絲帶 罷工撐醫護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848612</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4b620ca58b56e21eb1f8b98c4ebe5ca91ecb260e","tid":1848864,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"支持公安止暴制亂"},{"pid":"7bbd8a032cd2d151787cf64fa697e2be2265ef34","tid":1848864,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"支持屠村"},{"pid":"ebf03f7b7716008f511b8b97d919f57fce94db01","tid":1848864,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:05:37.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"32ab141b60a274e57a0429114c5bb29ef4ac36bd","tid":1848864,"uid":90328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ooF8Br87kjI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DooF8Br87kjI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=8d36b173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ooF8Br87kjI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n3分鐘版本from隔離post"},{"pid":"5f95d8b7ff4d96b7501cfb6244c38d28dc1a3590","tid":1848864,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"福建獨立"},{"pid":"6e4e5b80fadf437564e1ce9709f3475b138cb700","tid":1848864,"uid":11301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T17:08